description: This file declares functions and includes necessary headers for parsing and processing telemetry configuration data, particularly utilizing MessagePack and cJSON formats. It appears to define interfaces for configuration processing, MessagePack data extraction, and debugging.

methods.name: processConfiguration
methods.description: Parses configuration data from a string, associated with a profile name and hash, populating a Profile structure.

methods.name: msgpack_get_map_value
methods.description: Retrieves a value from a MessagePack map object by key.

methods.name: msgpack_get_array_element
methods.description: Retrieves an element from a MessagePack array by index.

methods.name: msgpack_strdup
methods.description: Duplicates a string from a MessagePack object.

methods.name: msgpack_print
methods.description: Prints a MessagePack object for debugging purposes.

methods.name: msgpack_strcmp
methods.description: Compares a MessagePack object with a string for equality.

methods.name: processMsgPackConfiguration
methods.description: Processes a MessagePack configuration object and populates a Profile structure.
